{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/full-report-ngintip-press-conference-studio-ghibli-di-jakarta-yuk/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Full Report: Ngintip Press Conference Studio Ghibli di Jakarta Yuk!","content":"<p>Saat CIAYO Blog datang ke Ballroom 3 tempat konferensi pers Studio Ghibli, rupanya pintu masih belum dibuka. Kami registrasi dulu sembari menikmati makanan ringan yang tersedia. Banyak pengunjung memilih untuk berkeliling. Rupanya mereka sedang mengagumi puluhan maket yang dipajang di luar Ballroom! Yup, semuanya adalah maket-maket karakter Studio Ghibli versi mini. Beberapa berupa tempat-tempat yang dijadikan latar belakang film karya studio Jepang itu.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_1738\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1738\" data-attachment-id=\"1738\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/full-report-ngintip-press-conference-studio-ghibli-di-jakarta-yuk/attachment/gambar-2-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-2-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"gambar-2-2\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-2-2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-2-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1738\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-2-2.jpg\" alt=\"Photo by CIAYO Picture\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-2-2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-2-2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1738\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Photo by CIAYO Pictures</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_1739\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1739\" data-attachment-id=\"1739\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/full-report-ngintip-press-conference-studio-ghibli-di-jakarta-yuk/attachment/gambar-3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"gambar-3\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Photo by CIAYO Picture&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1739\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-3.jpg\" alt=\"Photo by CIAYO Picture\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1739\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Photo by CIAYO Pictures</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_1741\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1741\" data-attachment-id=\"1741\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/full-report-ngintip-press-conference-studio-ghibli-di-jakarta-yuk/attachment/gambar-4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"gambar-4\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1741\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-4.jpg\" alt=\"Photo by CIAYO Picture\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1741\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Photo by CIAYO Pictures</p></div>\n<p>Pintu akhirnya terbuka dan kami berbondong-bondong masuk. Acara diawali dengan sosok cantik Sherina Munaf yang membawakan beberapa soundtrack populer dari Studio Ghibli, seperti Itsumo Nando Demo, Mononoke Hime, dan Tonari no Totoro.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_1742\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1742\" data-attachment-id=\"1742\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/full-report-ngintip-press-conference-studio-ghibli-di-jakarta-yuk/attachment/gambar-5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"gambar-5\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1742\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-5.jpg\" alt=\"Dia pikir~! Oh, salah lagu. Photo by CIAYO Picture\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1742\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Dia pikir~! Oh, salah lagu. Photo by CIAYO Pictures</p></div>\n<p>Eits, tapi ternyata tidak cuma Sherina yang tampil, loh. Ada pula Baim &#8220;The Dance Company&#8221; yang berduet bersama anaknya, Abbey Ibrahim. Dua bapak-anak ini membawakan lagu Ponyo dengan gaya yang imut! (Yang imut anaknya, ya, bukan bapaknya.)</p>\n<blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" style=\"background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 658px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);\" data-instgrm-captioned=\"\" data-instgrm-version=\"7\">\n<div style=\"padding: 8px;\">\n<div style=\"background: #F8F8F8; line-height: 0; margin-top: 40px; padding: 50.0% 0; text-align: center; width: 100%;\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin: 8px 0 0 0; padding: 0 4px;\"><a style=\"color: #000; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none; word-wrap: break-word;\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BSQ72rhj7xV/\" target=\"_blank\">There you go&#8230;abbey&#8217;s first timer with real crowd ?? #ghibliStudio #Ponyo #ghibli @theworldofghiblijkt Video by @refimonika Shouting by Zoe #AbbeyIbrahim</a></p>\n<p style=\"color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 8px; overflow: hidden; padding: 8px 0 7px; text-align: center; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;\">A post shared by Ibrahim Imran (@baimguitar) on <time style=\"font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px;\" datetime=\"2017-03-30T13:52:12+00:00\">Mar 30, 2017 at 6:52am PDT</time></p>\n</div>\n</blockquote>\n<p><script async defer src=\"//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js\"></script></p>\n<p>Anugerah kawaii mana lagi yang kau dustakan.</p>\n<p>Konferensi pers akhirnya dimulai dengan acara perkenalan sosok-sosok yang sudah berjasa dalam mewujudkan World of Ghibli di Indonesia. Willawati, CEO dari Kaninga Pictures, memaparkan jadwal penayangan film Studio Ghibli di Indonesia dengan rencana ekshibisi Studio Ghibli terbesar di Asia Tenggara.</p>\n<p>Di antaranya turut hadir pula Toshio Suzuki, Direktur Eksekutif Studio Ghibli. Pria Jepang berusia 68 tahun tersebut terlihat santai saat tampil menyapa penggemar Studi Ghibli dan awak media.</p>\n<p>Suzuki-san mengaku, ini adalah kunjungan keduanya ke Indonesia. Tahun lalu ia juga hadir saat penayangan terbatas film Spirited Away. “Sebelum saya datang ke sini, saya tidak tahu banyak tentang Indonesia. Saya sangat kaget ketika mendapatkan sambutan yang hangat dari penggemar Studio Ghibli di sini,” ujarnya sambil dibantu penerjemah.</p>\n<p>Ya, sambutan tahun lalu untuk Toshio Suzuki memang benar-benar meriah. Pasalnya, penayangan Spirited Away tahun lalu di Indonesia bertepatan dengan ulang tahun Toshio Suzuki. Fans Studio Ghibli dari seluruh Indonesia bekerja sama membawakan kue dan nasi tumpeng sebagai hadiah ulang tahun untuk Suzuki-san. Seru nggak sih? Sayang, kata Suzuki-san, “Saya tidak sempat makan kuenya.”</p>\n<p>Yah.</p>\n<p>Di tengah acara, MC tiba-tiba mengumumkan tamu yang sangat istimewa. Yup, siapa lagi kalau bukan Kaonashi? Sosok yang juga sering disebut No-Face dari film Spirited Away itu turut hadir di konferensi pers juga! Seluruh isi ruangan pun bersemangat menyambut karakter unik ini.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-video\" data-lang=\"en\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"in\">Waah! Ada sosok Kaonashi alias No Face dari film Spirited Away hadir di Jakarta! | <a href=\"https://twitter.com/angelinayetta\">@angelinayetta</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/WmQHlqkdgd\">pic.twitter.com/WmQHlqkdgd</a></p>\n<p>— Rappler Indonesia (@RapplerID) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RapplerID/status/847374706986565633\">March 30, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>Mas Kaonashi, yang hati-hati ya jalannya.</p>\n<p>Ketika diminta untuk memberi sambutan, Kaonashi akhirnya memberikan <em>speech</em> sebagai berikut:</p>\n<p>“A-ah. Ah.”</p>\n<p>Mengharukan.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_1745\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1745\" data-attachment-id=\"1745\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/full-report-ngintip-press-conference-studio-ghibli-di-jakarta-yuk/attachment/gambar-6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"gambar-6\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1745\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-6.jpg\" alt=\"Enak deh dipeluk sama Sherina. Photo by CIAYO Picture\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1745\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Enak deh dipeluk sama Sherina. Photo by CIAYO Pictures</p></div>\n<p>Acara dilanjutkan dengan <em>unveiling </em>logo World of Ghibli Jakarta yang resmi. Konon, Studio Ghibli mengaku puas dengan logo bikinan Bisri Mustova yang lebih sering dipanggil Mas Ova ini. Padahal mereka terkenal sangat ketat dengan desain-desain yang menyangkut materi Studio Ghibli, lho. Salut buat Mas Ova!</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_1746\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1746\" data-attachment-id=\"1746\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/full-report-ngintip-press-conference-studio-ghibli-di-jakarta-yuk/attachment/gambar-10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-10.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"gambar-10\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-10-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-10.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1746\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-10.jpg\" alt=\"So detailed. Design by Bisri Mustova\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-10.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-10-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1746\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">So detailed. Design by Bisri Mustova</p></div>\n<p>Sebelum mencapai penutupan konferensi pers, MC membuka sesi Q&amp;A. Rupanya banyak juga pertanyaan-pertanyaan dari awak media dan fans Studio Ghibli. Contohnya nih ya, ada yang bertanya seputar World of Ghibli itu sendiri, keterlibatan Sherina dengan Studio Ghibli, sampai film terbaru Hayao Miyazaki dan kesempatan voluntir serta <em>transfer knowledge</em> dari Studio Ghibli untuk industri kreatif Indonesia. Acara pun kemudian ditutup dengan foto bersama dan sesi tanda tangan oleh Toshio Suzuki.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_1747\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1747\" data-attachment-id=\"1747\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/full-report-ngintip-press-conference-studio-ghibli-di-jakarta-yuk/attachment/gambar-8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"gambar-8\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1747\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-8.jpg\" alt=\"Otsukare! Photo by CIAYO Picture\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-8.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-8-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1747\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Otsukare! Photo by CIAYO Pictures</p></div>\n<p>Demikian <em>full report</em> untuk konferensi pers Studio Ghibli di Ritz Carlton Kamis kemarin (30/3). Pingin tahu tentang isi Q&amp;A dan detil lebih jelas soal rangkaian acara World of Ghibli? Simak aja artikel-artikel selanjutnya di CIAYO Blog, gaes!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"cff48c8b-bdc8-5dd8-9f1d-ca6da6d8357f"}}}